Background

First documented canyoneering descent by Alden Anderson and Chris Abando. "I've wondered about this canyon for years, a few times while playing golf. Today I got to see what it was all about. I'd hoped it was a good candidate to run at night. Todays descent crushed all my hopes for that. A surprising number of rappels for the Verdugos." -AA
